                <head>The New Union Party</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Criticizes the enemies of the Democrats for attempting to create a
                    so-called Union Party. The Spirit asserts that this is just an underhanded trick
