            <div type="a">
                <column>5</column>
                <head>Your Ox or my Bull</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Demonstrates Republican hypocrisy by pointing out that a few weeks ago,
                    Republicans called it treasonous to criticize the Administration. Now, however,
                    as a result of Fremont's removal and other more conservative decisions, the
                    Republicans are attacking the very Administration they previously sought to
                    defend.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
